[This article highlights the need to vaccine large animals. I have said for a long time rabies vaccination of your animals is cheap insurance against a deadly disease. This becomes much more important if these are dairy animals, show animals, school project animals, or other large animals where humans have frequent or daily contact with them. - Mod.TG

